description: SPDR Bloomberg International Treasury Bond ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Bloomberg Global Treasury ex-US Capped Index (the "Index")Seeks to provide exposure to fixed-rate local currency sovereign debt of investment grade countries outside the United StatesIndex includes government bonds issued by investment grade countries outside the United States, in local currencies, that have a remaining maturity of one year or more and are rated investment gradeRebalanced on the last business day of the month
name: SPDR Bloomberg International Treasury Bond ETF
